properties.name: Aunt Linda's home
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard357 N. 900 W. Salt Lake City, UTDuring my life, this house was home to my mother\'s parents. At various times my uncle Rick, who died from diabetic complications at age 28 in 1992, lived here with his wife Stacy and their children Daniel, Jessica, and Amanda. A guy named Don also once lived here with my grandparents. After my Grandma Mass died from stroke complications in 1997 my aunt Linda lived here to take care of Grandpa Mass who passed away in 2002. Aunt Linda still lives here on her own.

properties.name: Council Thrift Shop
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard 1127 SW Morrison St. Portland, ORThis is where I\'ve worked since May, 2005. It\'s the coolest real thrift store in town, and a great place to meet crazy people.

properties.name: Davenport College on the Yale Campus
properties.description: Posted by AswoodardNew Haven, CTStayed in this residential college for a month in July of 1999 with the Junior Statesmen of America. It was an odd but telling experience.

properties.name: Fairdale, IL
properties.description: Posted by AswoodardFairdale, ILThis is where my father grew up and was the hometown to many of my ancestors. It\'s population today is 152.

properties.name: Grandma Woodard's residence
properties.description: Posted by AswoodardN. Mulford Rd. Rockford, ILThis is the Christian Life Retirement Community where my father\'s mother, Dorothy Woodard lives. I\'ve stayed there a number of times over the last several years while visiting.

properties.name: Hotel Opera
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard C/ Cuesta de Santo Domingo, 2 Madrid, SpainWhen I was in Madrid in March, 1998, this is where I stayed with my school group.

properties.name: Jason and Christine's Place
properties.description: Posted by AswoodardAurora, ILThis is where my cousin Jason Woodard and his wife Christine currently live, and I stayed there on my most recent visit. They\'re planning to move to DeKalb once they have their first child after this summer.

properties.name: Jewett Hall
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard380 Boyer Ave. Walla Walla, WAThis building is one of the main freshman dorms at Whitman College. My room was 101, and I lived here all freshman year with my roommate Jeff Ives. Our section was called the Pit.

properties.name: My family's first home.
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard  11189 N. Donley Dr. Parker, COMy mom, dad, and I lived here from my birth till New Year\'s Eve 1989. Parker had about 500 people when my parents bought the house and about 5,000 when we left. Have no idea who lives there now. Many memories.

properties.name: North Hall
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard380 Boyer Ave. Walla Walla, WAI lived here the first semester of my sophomore year on the second floor. North Hall was converted from a hospital into dorms so though it looks nice on the outside it is too cavernous inside to feel homey in my opinion. I was glad to move out.

properties.name: Our home in Tigard
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard 8469 SW Ashford St. Tigard, ORWe moved here from the rental place in Lake Oswego on Labor Day 1990 and my parents still live here.

properties.name: Pine Lane Primary School
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard 6475 East Ponderosa Dr. Parker, COMy first school. Was in Mrs. Krebs\' (?) kindergarten class - \'87-\'88. Mrs. Swain\'s first grade \'88-\'89 and Miss Page\'s second grade in \'89 before my family moved to Oregon. The playground was dangerous and fun when I was there. Slides with rusty edges that dropped off on hard-packed dirt, wooden playsets that splintered and iced over breaking skin and skulls left and right.

properties.name: Rose Medical Center in Denver, CO
properties.description: Posted by AswoodardEast 9th Ave. Denver, COBorn 2/4/1982 at this hospital to Beverly and Dana Woodard one month after they were married.

properties.name: The Light House
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard380 Boyer Ave. Walla Walla, WAI lived here senior year of college with Ben Garbee, Peter Biskind, Peter Baker, and Chris McKearin. It was a good house inspite of us.

properties.name: The rental house
properties.description: Posted by AswoodardSW 63rd Ave. Lake Oswego, ORMy parents rented this house for the first six months we lived in Oregon in 1990 until we moved to Tigard.

properties.name: Where I currently live
properties.description: Posted by Aswoodard6646 SW Capitol Hwy. Portland, ORI\'ve lived here since August, 2005. It\'s nice.
